736
01:42:04,291 --> 01:42:07,408
Police! Drop! Drop, or I'll fire!

737
01:42:19,131 --> 01:42:25,570
And so to their final rest do we commit
these two and entrust them unto our Lord.

738
01:42:26,931 --> 01:42:31,846
In the name of the Father, and of the Son,
and of the Holy Ghost. Amen.

739
01:42:32,611 --> 01:42:34,602
Detail, attention!

740
01:42:35,611 --> 01:42:37,602
Present arms!

741
01:42:41,331 --> 01:42:43,845
Ready, aim, fire!

742
01:42:45,651 --> 01:42:47,881
Ready, aim, fire!

743
01:42:49,851 --> 01:42:52,160
Ready, aim, fire!

744
01:43:46,451 --> 01:43:50,842
Excuse me, Mr President. When you're ready
